{{ja-kanji|grade=4|rs=日05}}

# [[yesterday]]; last, past (day, week, month, year, etc.)

subSections.title: Compounds
subSections.text:
* {{ja-r|昨日|きのう}}: [[yesterday]]
* {{ja-r|昨%週|さく%しゅう}}: [[last week]]
* {{ja-r|昨%月|さく%げつ}}: [[last month]]
* {{ja-r|昨%年|さく%ねん}}: [[last year]]
* {{ja-r|昨%春|さく%しゅん}}: [[last spring]]
* {{ja-r|昨%夏|さく%なつ}}: [[last summer]]
* {{ja-r|昨%秋|さく%しゅう}}: [[last autumn]]
* {{ja-r|昨%冬|さく%とう}}: [[last winter]]
